short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Browser extension for Anybox. Collect your links and images.
short.zh_CN: Anybox fo Mac的浏览器扩展，轻松收集链接和图片。

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Use this extension to easily save links, text and files to Anybox Mac app.

You can configure if you want to show the checkmark for existing links in Options page.

* This extension is only applicable on macOS and requires the running of Anybox for macOS app.
long.zh_CN:
使用此扩展保存链接或文本到Anybox for macOS应用。

可在选项页配置是否显示当前页面的指示。

* 此扩展仅适用macOS平台，且需Anybox for macOS在运行状态。
